snippet.title: One Lonely Outpost Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
It's here! The One Lonely Outpost Kickstarter is live, and with it a trailer showing just a few bits of what you can expect. Back us now!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/aurorianstudios/one-lonely-outpost
You can also join us on:
Discord: https://discord.gg/anxEG5t
Twitter: https://twitter.com/1LonelyOutpost
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/onelonelyoutpost/
Instegram: https://www.instagram.com/onelonelyoutpost/
